{"tid":977634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"戴耳機走鐵軌...少年不知有火車　下秒遭撞死影片曝光","createTime":"2019-01-11T10:18:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-11T10:56:40.000Z","uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c63e52bfbf4957c1129ea9f5a5c5af86b7c62eeb","tid":977634,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T10:18:35.000Z","msg":"烏茲別克一名少年日前戴著耳機聽音樂，走在鐵軌上，不料一輛火車疾駛而來，他沒聽到鳴笛聲，當場遭火車撞飛身亡。<br />\n <br />\n據《俄羅斯新聞社》報導，5日下午1點多，這一輛火車行經烏茲別克努庫斯時，駕駛發現前方有一個人走在鐵軌上，於是緊急鳴笛煞車，但火車還是撞上他，影片中可以聽到當下發出巨大撞擊聲，少年當場不治。<br />\n <br />\n這名17歲的少年因為戴耳機聽音樂，因此沒注意到有火車。事故發生的影片也在網路上流傳，目前執法機構正在調查此事件。"},{"pid":"ed436bad10e7a4891dd8e6d94e66d18813b79a48","tid":977634,"uid":1221,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T10:19:20.000Z","msg":"片？"},{"pid":"d325cbbd992c84d4d0f5fb8b538fb672fad928cf","tid":977634,"uid":13992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T10:19:49.000Z","msg":"片呢？"},{"pid":"ee6bef1fc3b241859ae80d5d8fc2c84762521c6f","tid":977634,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T10:20:26.000Z","msg":"吊你<br />\n以為真係有片👊"},{"pid":"ccf01512eebdb8aba3d4855a3c7f2927ebd0ac8e","tid":977634,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T10:20:45.000Z","msg":"隔音又幾好"},{"pid":"4d8aca6d1d0a6803fdbee9b79e5fd3333d931c7a","tid":977634,"uid":131522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T10:20:50.000Z","msg":"片呢樓豬？"},{"pid":"f3bba1fe5d446c99e78531ef79d85ab0134de421","tid":977634,"uid":25002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T10:20:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0ba3a9876409764879d66bb035438adc610b0f10","tid":977634,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T10:21:34.000Z","msg":"對耳筒應該好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e09d6fc38bbdf3d6143f63121bbedbe9938bb2f","tid":977634,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0